OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury reveal new
OL,4,Cson's name during boxing fight
OL,6,FMolly-Mae Hague and Tommy Fury have
OL,7,Frevealed their newborn son's name is
OL,8,FMidas Fury.
OL,10,FBoxer Fury confirmed the name on
OL,11,FSaturday night as he stepped into the
OL,12,Fring for his showdown with Eddie Hall
OL,13,Fin Manchester.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
