OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury reveal new
OL,4,Cson's name during boxing fight
OL,6,FMidas was written in big letters on
OL,7,Fthe front of Fury's shorts, ending
OL,8,Fweeks of speculation from fans of the
OL,9,Fcouple, who met on Love Island in 2019.
OL,11,FThe unusual name originates from Greek
OL,12,Fmythology, and is best recognised
OL,13,Fthrough the story of King Midas, whose
OL,14,Ftouch turned everything to gold.
OL,16,FFury, who won his fight against Hall,
OL,17,Falso had his daughter's name, Bambi,
OL,18,Fwritten on the back of his shorts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
