OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury reveal new
OL,4,Cson's name during boxing fight
OL,6,FAfterwards, he pulled on an England
OL,7,Fshirt with 'Midas' and the number two
OL,8,Fwritten on the back, while Hague
OL,9,Fwatched ringside.
OL,11,F"This was for my new baby son, Midas,"
OL,12,FFury told the crowd after his win.
OL,13,F"Welcome to the world!"
OL,15,FThe three ringside judges scored the
OL,16,Fsix-round fight 59-56, 58-56, 57-57.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
