OL,3,CMolly-Mae and Tommy Fury reveal new
OL,4,Cson's name during boxing fight
OL,6,FFury and Hague welcomed their daughter
OL,7,FBambi together in January 2023, with
OL,8,FHague announcing she was pregnant with
OL,9,Ftheir second child in February this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FThe pair then revealed they had
OL,13,Fwelcomed baby Midas with an Instagram
OL,14,Fpost on June 3, which featured the
OL,15,Ftrio admiring their baby in a black
OL,16,Fand white photograph.
OL,18,FThe caption read: "...and then there
OL,19,Fwere 4."
